-- Finmeccanica to offer $5.26 billion for DRS: source
-- 
-- Mon May 12, 2008 6:37pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/12/us-drs-finmeccanica-bid-idUSL1226765820080512

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Italian aerospace company Finmeccanica Spa ( SIFI.MI ) is to make a friendly takeover bid worth 3.4 billion euros ($5.26 billion) for DRS Technologies Inc DRS.N of the United States, sources close to the deal said late on Monday. 

 Sources said the board of Finmeccanica, in which the Italian Treasury has a nearly 34 percent stake, had decided the details of the offer at a seven-hour board meeting. No other details were immediately available.